OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShops face challenging     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fyear, says industry body   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Shops across the country are facing a  
OL,6, particularly difficult six months ahead
OL,7, as customers try to cope with higher   
OL,8, prices by buying less, according to the
OL,9, body representing UK retailers.        
OL,11,FSales will only rise by 2.3% at most in
OL,12,Fthe first half of the year, the British
OL,13,FRetail Consortium (BRC) predicts.      
OL,15,FBut sales should pick up in the second 
OL,16,Fhalf of the year, the BRC said.        
OL,18,FRetailers are also facing higher costs,
OL,19,Fand government support for firms'      
OL,20,Fenergy bills is due to end in March.   
